---
title: Middle Eastern-Inspired Turkey Bowls with Hummus and Savoury Rice
description: Creamy, spicy, tart, savoury – this delicious Middle Eastern-inspired dish has it all! Speedy shawarma-spiced rice is jewelled with onions, then topped with fragrant turkey, hummus and marinated tomatoes.
